{{Italic title}}{{Infobox film|name=The Scarlet Letter|image=|caption=|writer=[[Byun Hyuk]] <br/> Kang Hyeon-joo|starring=[[Han Suk-kyu]]<br />[[Lee Eun-ju]]<br />[[Sung Hyun-ah]]<br />[[Uhm Ji-won]]|director=[[Byun Hyuk]]|producer=Lee Seung-jae|cinematography=Choe Hyeon-gi|editing=Hahm Sung-won|music=Lee Jae-jin|distributor=[[Showbox]]|released={{Start date|2004|10|28}}|country=Koonfur Kuuriya|runtime=118 daqiiqado|language=Kuuriyan|budget=|native_name=}}'''''The Scarlet Letter''''' waa 2004 filim [[Filimada xiisaha|xiise]] oo [[Shineemada Koonfur Kuuriya|Koonfur Kuuriya ah]], ku saabsan dambi baare booliis ah oo baara kiiska dilka isagoo ku dhibtoonaya inuu ku xirnaado xiriirkiisa xaaskiisa iyo marwadiisa. Waa filimkii labaad ee Byun Hyuk (Daniel H. Byun), oo jilay [[Han Suk-kyu]], [[Lee Eun-ju]], [[Sung Hyun-ah]] iyo [[Uhm Ji-won]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Kim|first=Tae-jong|title=Scarlet Letter: Love, Murder by the Numbers|url=http://www.hancinema.net/scarlet-letter-love-murder-by-the-numbers-1587.html|work=[[The Korea Times]] via [[Hancinema]]|accessdate=2013-09-03|date=7 October 2004}}</ref> Filimku wuxuu ka soo baxay filimkii ugu dambeeyay ee 2004 [[Filimka Caalamiga ee Busan Dabaaldag]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Thacker|first=Todd|title=Korea's 9th Busan Film Festival Wins Big|url=http://english.ohmynews.com/articleview/article_view.asp?at_code=215174|work=[[OhmyNews International]]|accessdate=2013-09-03|date=15 October 2004}}</ref> Filimku wuxuu ku salaysan yahay sheekooyinka gaagaaban ee Kim Young-ha ''A Meditation On Mirror'' iyo ''Photo Shop Murder''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cine21.com/news/view/?mag_id=26825|title=끝없는 욕망의 원죄, <주홍글씨>|date=2004-10-26|publisher=Cine21|accessdate=2016-09-22|language=Korean}}</ref> 

In kasta oo Lee Eun-ju uu waayo-aragnimo hore u lahaa muujinta galmada iyo [[Qaawanaanta ee filimanta|qaawanaanta]] ''[[Virgin Stripped Bare by Her Bachelors]]'' (2000), Waxay la kulantay indho-indhaynta saxaafadda Koonfur Kuuriya iyo [[Isticmaalayaasha internetka|netizen-ka]], ee loogu talagalay muuqaallada galmada ee qiirada badan iyo "muuqaalka [[jirridda]]" ee ku jira ''The Scarlet Letter'' kaas oo loo arko “mid ka mid ah muuqaallada ugu naxdinta badan uguna daran taariikhda filimka Kuuriya."<ref>{{cite web|last=Kim|first=Gab-sik|title=The Scarlet Letter|url=http://english.donga.com/srv/service.php3?biid=2004102101828&path_dir=20041021|work=[[The Dong-a Ilbo]]|accessdate=2013-09-03|date=20 October 2004}}</ref> Waxaa la qiyaasayaa doorkeeda dalbashada iyo indha-indheynta dadweynaha, waxay ku biirisay oo ay ku dul habsatay arrimo kala duwan oo qoys, dhaqaale, shaqo, iyo hurdo la'aan ah. [[Niyadjabka|Niyad-jabkeedii]] ba’anaa wuxuu ku dhammaaday is -dilid bishii Febraayo 2005.<ref>{{cite web|title=Top Actress Lee Eun-ju's Suicide Shocks Nation|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2005/02/22/2005022261032.html|work=[[The Chosun Ilbo]]|accessdate=2013-09-03|date=22 February 2005}}</ref>

Agaasime Kim Ki-duk, oo aan ku cusbayn muranka ku saabsan aflaamtiisa, ayaa laga soo xigtay majaladda filinka Shiinaha "Movie Watch" (看 電影) isagoo si gaar ah u xusaya ''The Scarlet Letter'' oo ka mid ah dramaada Kuuriya ee sanadihii ugu dambeeyay. Kadib wuxuu tuuray [[Sung Hyun-ah]], oo caan ku noqotay doorkeedii ''The Scarlet Letter'', sidii halyeeygii ''[[Time]]''.

Filimkii lagu soo bandhigay Jaban, aktarada ruug-caddaaga ah ee Kumiko Akiyoshi ayaa ammaantay qaab-dhismeedka hoggaanka waxaana ay barbardhigtay filimka mid taariikhi ah ''[[Basic Instinct]]'' iyo ''[[Fatal Attraction]]''.<ref>[http://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/1144355/ "Introductory dialogue at the Japanese premiere of The Scarlet Letter"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/1144355/ |date=20081221224158 }}. ''[[Livedoor]]. 11 May 2005. Retrieved 2013-09-03.''</ref>

